OL,3,CWRU proposes cutting rugby regions to
OL,4,Cthree or two
OL,6,FThe Welsh Rugby Union (WRU) has
OL,7,Flaunched a consultation over a major
OL,8,Fshakeup to Welsh rugby that could cut
OL,9,Fregional clubs from the current four
OL,10,Fto three or two.
OL,12,FThe restructure would be carried out
OL,13,Fin time for the 2027/28 season.
OL,15,FThe consultation with the sides -
OL,16,FScarlets, Ospreys, Cardiff Rugby and
OL,17,FDragons - will take place over August
OL,18,Fand September along with the
OL,19,Finvolvement of other stakeholders.
